{"tid":401053,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"死肥閪肥佬咪撚坐小巴啦仆街","createTime":"2017-09-15T10:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T12:23:29.000Z","uid":107733,"like":45,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"740335b811ccc09889857e799718f7b1161e4b06","tid":401053,"uid":107733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:05:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老味<br />\n成坐山咁撚大份<br />\n一個人坐1.5個位<br />\n我有半邊腳都要伸出去<br />\n最撚慘佢坐入面<br />\n大支野咁當先到先得<br />\n坐左你半個位都無心要讓開少少<br />\n係連少少都無呀<br />\n當正自己係大爺咁撚樣<br />\n無恥到仆街<br />\n仲要d死肥閪死肥鳩都係好撚臭<br />\n坐佢地隔離真係慘過食屎<br />\n屌哂你班仆街<br />\n要求公共交通工具肥人收1.5倍車費<br />\n同意請分享及正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebbe4fb9c2f9a6aaf1ec8c1e23cae5dd7309516","tid":401053,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:06:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2bc0432de15583fe1f211d4299d8bd4ce1d0c911","tid":401053,"uid":24824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:06:46.000Z","msg":"AGGER<br />\n今朝比個肥嬸霸撚哂個位"},{"pid":"14f5f892fd18c27e0258b1f2a65e33db6cf2c3c4","tid":401053,"uid":107733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:07:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係都要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />✌🏻</blockquote><br />\n收皮啦死肥閪<br />\n影響到人你有冇羞恥心架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858c9807076b5d9bccf78a1d4b03f3816d4b02d2","tid":401053,"uid":30510,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:09:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係都要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />✌🏻</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係✘喺✓<br />\n都✘嘟✓<br />\n要✘喓✓<br />\n坐✘唑✓</span>"},{"pid":"95a8610d6c10f6a960b3695df67c67f4110c1742","tid":401053,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:11:03.000Z","msg":"你坐入面仲死呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />